Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:07.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爱恋是惊悚 冲击 悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无形的力量 依靠着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:18.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请不要紧闭你的心扉 紧紧地…紧紧地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在坚定无比的内心里充满推理的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.53,0:00:22.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}永远以最坚强的节奏揭开案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.36,0:00:24.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k182}今天的事件不同寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.01,0:00:26.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}生意兴隆的餐厅是整个事件的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.36,0:00:36.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}或许我也想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.85,0:00:46.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让你感受到与我相同感受的刺痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.06,0:00:53.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是什么让自己心痛 是什么让自己畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}纠葛不清的二人真实面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}害怕去面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爱恋是惊悚 冲击 悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.01,0:01:14.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使困惑随着清风飞逝 想永远躺在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你小小的胸膛里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.72,0:01:21.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请不要紧闭你的心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.29,0:01:25.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使对于自己的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.81,0:01:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有着新的迷惘与不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}生意兴隆的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.22,0:01:54.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一个奇怪的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}伦太郎你们家好像是开餐厅的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道 店名叫“饱餐饭店”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.13,0:02:07.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们家餐厅又黑又脏 不管什么都好难吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以无论什么时候去都没有几个客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.22,0:02:11.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k101}你说的那个叔叔怎么奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是在两个月前突然跑到我家店里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我叫龟仓雄二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}府上过世的老先生对我曾经有再造之恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对你有再造之恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}这份大恩大德实在一言难尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}所以说 为了报答他的这份恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}希望你们能够答应我 从今天开始住在这里工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.28,0:02:39.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k109}住在这里工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k117}你要住在我们这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}可是我们没有钱再请员工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我不用你们给我薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}我只是想报恩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以后请多指教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}好了 我开始报恩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}从那天起 他就这样在我们家住下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 他一定有什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}因为 我去世的爷爷以前脾气很坏而且小气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根本就不是那种会对别人施恩的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个叔叔到我们家来一定是别有居心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k299}所以 我想请你们少年侦探团帮忙调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我还以为是什么有趣的案子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来只是要调查一个满口胡说骗吃骗住的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我可以感觉到非常强的犯罪气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:32.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也感觉到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k133}没错 这味道非常强烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}灰原…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}好 我们少年侦探团出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}加油啊 江户川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不好意思 我还有点事要处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}不要逃啊 灰原 你太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这真的是饱餐饭店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}有什么不对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k105}现在店里不但变得好干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.51,0:04:08.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}而且…而且店里还有这么多客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会这样全是因为那个叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天店里还是没有一个客人来光顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们家哪一天不是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为现在好吃又干净的餐厅太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样下去就糟了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 我以前正好受过厨师训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我从现在开始教店长料理技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}另外 店面也要重新装潢一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}重新装潢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}这个费用由我来出就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}你们不要跟我客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我只是想尽我所能的报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就这样 店里的生意奇迹般的越来越好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这有什么奇怪的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}他不是说是为了报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}才自己拿钱出来重新装潢店面的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看他完全就是个好人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}我知道了 他一定是想先让生意好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.46,0:05:14.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}等赚了钱 再把你们的钱全部偷走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这真的是他的目的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}如果要等生意好起来才能偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}就不会先让店里赚钱再来偷钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}直接去偷那些赚钱的店不是更快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:26.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k117}真是的 还说什么有犯罪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.17,0:05:33.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.94,0:05:38.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}新菜单研究中 绝对禁止进入 龟仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个啊 龟仓叔叔现在每天从早到晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}都在那里为我们的餐厅研究新的菜单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他说在完成之前必须保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}所以连我们都不能进那个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}伦太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}好了 现在店里正忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}既然回来了就赶快帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}跟你同学说再见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}只要店里生意好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}这家人就自然一整天都不会回到客厅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.76,0:06:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}他正好可以自己一个人待在客厅里面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道是《红发会》里的那种伎俩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.47,0:06:22.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}这是《红发会》里的作案手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对啊 红发会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}那是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k243}《红发会》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}是福尔摩斯探案全集60多个故事中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}最有名的故事之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}有个男子以店员的身份混进一家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}花言巧语把店长骗出去之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}他就趁机从那家店的地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}朝着银行的方向挖出一条地道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.62,0:06:50.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}最后把银行的钱偷了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}这是一个主题新颖 手法大胆的犯罪故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是谢谢你告诉大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.78,0:07:03.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}话说回来 这个故事已经有一百多年的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在根本就没有那种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k162}有耐心为了偷钱去挖地道的罪犯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他在挖地道的话 一定会有声音的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}够了 这样子难看死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}要想确定这点 我会想办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}你怎么确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.22,0:07:33.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:34.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}应该是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}什么事啊 伦太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}叔叔 不好意思打扰你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}我们听说叔叔来了之后 餐厅生意就好起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那叔叔简直就是财神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}所以我们想来看看财神的手相 可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看我的手相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.22,0:07:53.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}你们尽管看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}不会是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 他的手相说他会犯罪对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我不是想看他的手相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}他手上一大堆老茧和水泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是使用铲子的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}虽然难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不过他的确是在挖掘地道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}我不是早就说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}光彦好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是可惜 这次功劳都被光彦抢去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 世上真的会有这种事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.90,0:08:35.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k78}先得查出他在朝什么地方挖掘地道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.03,0:08:39.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k82}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 距离饱餐饭店最近的银行就是这家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 今天没有营业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这家银行 从一个星期以前就停业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.89,0:08:57.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}那就不是这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.26,0:09:03.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又猜错了哦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这附近还会有哪里可能作为目标的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看 这里有一家珠宝店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不管有多厉害的小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}都别想从我们这里把宝石偷出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.71,0:09:24.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}我们这里装了目前世界上最先进的保安系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以前的错误不会再犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}以前的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}我们这里以前曾经被偷过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}当时一批价值三亿元的珠宝被偷走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那名犯人到现在都还没有被抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}珠宝大盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}而且到现在都还没有被抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.98,0:09:43.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}你们上次被偷大概是在多久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到下个月就整整五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就应该不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}珠宝大盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}然后是在秘密挖掘地道的可疑男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.39,0:10:01.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}光彦 你该不会真的那么认为吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}好了 我得去工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.34,0:10:15.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}你问了些什么 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}我已经把这个谜题完全解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我认为伦太郎他们家那个龟仓叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}就是五年前到刚才那家珠宝店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}偷走了价值三亿元珠宝的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}珠宝大盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.24,0:10:32.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k151}我的推理绝对不会有错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k151}不过你的推理有太多地方说不通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 这个犯人也不是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}偷了珠宝立刻变卖出去 警方马上就能查到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}将赃物一直带在身边行动又太危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以 他在偷了珠宝之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}就先找了一个地方 把珠宝埋了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.22,0:11:02.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个地方就是当时伦太郎家里做重建工程的地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们家曾经做过重建工程啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你就是在向阿姨问这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.28,0:11:14.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没错 这个犯人等到五年之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以店员的身份住进他家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}就可以神不知鬼不地把珠宝挖出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好厉害啊 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}这个推理太完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}你们这么说 我都不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}真有你的 其实我心里也是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}他为什么要等了五年以后才来挖出珠宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不知道吗 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}当然是为了等法律追诉期过去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}盗窃案的追诉期是五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}也就是说 这个犯人很快就可以拿着珠宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大摇大摆地找人到处变卖去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}五年是指刑事案件的追诉期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}民事案件的追诉期是二十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}也就是说 他现在挖出来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}那批珠宝也还不能算是他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么复杂的法律规定 我们怎么会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}连我们都不知道的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那个犯人当然也不可能知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}你还真是吹毛求疵 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我妈妈经常跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}我们做人一定要老实一点才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这根本就是两回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.79,0:12:26.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}我们现在就把那个珠宝大盗送到警局去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:27.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k56}不行 还没有证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}这样只会自取其辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.20,0:12:32.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}我当然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k85}只要逮到他犯案的瞬间 这总行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你想干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}当然是设陷阱抓他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}设陷阱 拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么 又是你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.72,0:12:58.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}又要看手相了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}我们已经全知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.75,0:13:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.77,0:13:08.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k103}你怎么掩饰也瞒不过我们少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来 我们只要等他自己上当就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你这算什么陷阱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}他一定会很快就害怕得露出狐狸尾巴来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.51,0:13:30.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}一定会成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.71,0:13:34.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k75}哪个大人会被几个小学生恐吓而害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.44,0:13:41.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k66}你们全家要去温泉度假两天一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是龟仓叔叔昨天晚上突然建议爸爸他们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他说店里生意好起来之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}我们一直都没有好好度过假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}就算在外面住一夜也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}还说我们回来之后 工作的热情会更高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}依我看 他一定不跟你们一起去 对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他说不想打搅我们一家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他让他们一家人全都出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}一定是想趁这个时候一口气把珠宝都挖出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}我看就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}怎么样 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}他真的上了我们的当 露出狐狸尾巴来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.09,0:14:20.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可能 真的有这种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我还是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来 你好像很烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}本来就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}哪会有因为小学生威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}就慌慌张张露出马脚的犯人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}不可理解的还不止这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}比如…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k117}工藤 这一次的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.41,0:14:50.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}不同于你以前对付过的 那些工于心计的罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}有什么不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k219}他是个单纯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这我就更不懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.45,0:15:05.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来 这次柯南的自信心受到了很大打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为这次英雄完全无用武之地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他会不会从此开始自暴自弃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我觉得很有这个可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.69,0:15:17.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}那就糟了 我们可不能让朋友这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你真的不一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k82}我朋友要我一定要到他那里去住一个晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}祝你们旅途愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以前我做梦也想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}我们一家子竟然可以一起去温泉旅游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}这都是托我们生意越来越好的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}不 托龟仓老弟的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}真多亏了他这个实在的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好了 他们全都出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来 我们就等龟仓叔叔回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果他一直不回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}我们就在这里等一个晚上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}你们都是怎么跟家里说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}看 他真的回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来 我们只要在外面等一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.08,0:16:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}再用伦太郎借给我们的钥匙一起冲进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就可以逮到他把珠宝挖出来的那一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}柯南 你好像没什么精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我每天都这么拼命地挖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}怎么到现在还没有挖出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}早知道当年就不要因为一时冲动埋得这么深了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.04,0:16:39.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}挖到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.83,0:16:45.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}我的珠宝 我的珠宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被你埋藏的这批珠宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}我们刚才看得一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}你别这样 我们也不是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}快点干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}对犯人说明你整个推理的经过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个最出风头的工作让给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为你这次几乎都没什么表现的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}现在根本没有必要说明推理的经过嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}快点 交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}加油啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.10,0:17:40.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}龟仓先生 你就是五年前那个溜进米花珠宝店里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}偷走价值三亿元珠宝的珠宝大盗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}完全正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}看吧 他一下就承认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}不过 我也不是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}我知道立刻拿去变卖的话 一定会被警方追缉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以 我事先就挑好了地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}就在当时这户人家正在进行重建的地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}把这批珠宝埋起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后 我为了避免引起警方怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}非常努力地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}不管师傅怎么责骂刁难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}我都忍了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}我的同事都因为受不了师傅严格的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}放弃了料理这行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}但是我忍下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}五年 只要再熬五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}那批价值三亿元的珠宝 就是属于我的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我就是因为心里抱着这个希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}所以不管多么艰苦的训练 我都能忍受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.16,0:18:31.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k83}我日夜期待的这一天 终于快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}我实在等不到法律追诉期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}连一秒都忍不住 就想把它挖出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}你认为只要以店员的身份来这里工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}就有机会将那批珠宝挖出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是你估计错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}这家餐厅没什么客人光顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}生意冷清得门可罗雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}所以他们一家人平常没事就待在客厅里看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再这样下去 不管你等多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}都很难有机会把宝石挖出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你决定 用自己的钱将店面重新装潢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再把你所学的料理技巧教给店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}店里的生意果然有了好转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.35,0:19:14.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k225}你终于成功地把他们全家人从客厅赶到了餐厅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.15,0:19:16.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}你就可以把全部精力放在挖掘珠宝的工作上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这样的吧 龟仓雄二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一切就像你说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.03,0:19:28.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k72}我们几个的推理真是天衣无缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}但是我实在无法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天不过是几个小学生威胁你罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k225}为什么你就乱了手脚 急着要把它挖出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我胆子比较小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}虽然是小学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}可是听到“侦探团”我就开始害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}这有什么好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k129}你一个大人怕一个小不点的侦探团像话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}既然你能想出让他们去温泉旅游这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么一开始的时候不使用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你根本不用把店面重新装潢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}让餐厅生意好起来这么大费周折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}一开始就送他们一张旅游招待券当做礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k243}不但更快 也更省钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.12,0:20:13.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}这样不就轻而易举地让他们一家人到外面去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你这么说也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}那你为什么不做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}我没想到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.77,0:20:30.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}灰原同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}你认输了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.01,0:20:34.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}我不是说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}这一次的对手是个非常单纯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们好像到了 是我报的警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这次会不会得到警政总监奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}要是能得到就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}我想你们一定会得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}毕竟这是大功一件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}也没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.01,0:21:08.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}气死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}我连一点解决案件后的成就感都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这种案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}我最讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.09,0:21:29.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然未来 不全都是美好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.43,0:21:45.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可以确定的是现在 正迈向未来 比任何人更耀眼地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.11,0:22:01.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}站在这里 即使是为了 即将粉碎的现实而流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}We can start in my life 一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.26,0:22:12.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}伴随着永不放弃的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.22,0:22:24.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 就因为可以遇见 另一个自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.86,0:22:31.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能将心情 转变成唯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.83,0:22:37.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看 让我们就从这里开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.16,0:22:42.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Just start in my life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}由于在法律追诉期之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}协助警方将珠宝大盗缉捕到案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}我们得到了警方颁发的感谢状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.18,0:22:56.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们这次表现得真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}这次很简单地解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有件事情我要告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是每次的犯人都会这么笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}几个小鬼头去揭发他的罪行 实在太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以后你们要谨慎一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.55,0:23:16.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}这真不像柯南你平常会说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.74,0:23:18.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.91,0:23:21.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k117}这次功劳被我们抢走了 你就这么不甘心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.13,0:23:24.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}元太 你怎么可以这样说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}柯南已经受了很大的打击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.41,0:23:30.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 你要快点打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.02,0:23:33.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}都是我不好 柯南 别难过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.86,0:23:36.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k122}我的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}是用在那种跟狡猾的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.35,0:23:40.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}斗智的时候会爆出火花的案件上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.97,0:23:44.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}像这种小案件我才不屑破呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}下回 久违的园子将登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}啊 好久不见 大家好 我是园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}格斗游戏的陷阱（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}死…死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}游戏角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}谁啊
